properties.Name: DunBradstreetEmployeeRangeDesignation
properties.Description:
Some companies do not lend themselves to a Dun & Bradstreet rating.  Instead reports on these business carry an Employee Range Designation (ER) which is indicative of size based on number of employees. 

ER   No. of Employees 
-----------------------------------
ER1 = 1000 and above 
ER2 = 500-999
ER3 = 100-499
ER4 = 50-99
ER5 = 21-49
ER6 = 10-19
ER7 = 5-9
ER8 = 1-4
ERN = Not Available
